{
  "stem": "14810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The only good thing about it was it was cold, bitter cold, but we worked in-- in the mountains, in there, so it wasn't-- so it wasn't too cold.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were there till April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Health?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was still in good health.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was still in good health.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were there till about April.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About April.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the orders came again, move again, because from every direction-- the Americans came at it from this side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said they have to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put us again on trains, and they moved us to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was still wasn't occupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't still by the-- by neither one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember we stopped near Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was April the 20th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the reason I remember this well because April the 20th was Hitler's birthday, and the SS came and they gave us extra piece of margarine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in honor of the Fuhrer, they said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a Friday morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this time we were in-- in closed train, a closed cattle train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and we weren't-- they just packed us like-- there were about 80 of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was still in-- although it was very cold outside, but inside was very hot, you know, with so many people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So most of us took off our clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had-- all I had is my shorts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "About 8 o'clock, just before we started-- give us the-- something to eat, the alarm sounded, and it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, you could see swarms of planes, American fighter planes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they swooped down and they strafed our train, because they didn't know that-- they thought maybe it's soldiers, German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
